        <updateDate>2021-07-06T12:04:09Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Jonny Wade Pediatric Cancer Research Act</b></p> <p>This bill terminates (1) the taxpayer election to designate $3 of income tax liability for financing of presidential election campaigns, (2) the Presidential Election Campaign Fund, and (3) the Presidential Primary Matching Payment Account.</p> <p>The Department of the Treasury must transfer the funds remaining in the Presidential Election Campaign Fund to the 10-Year Pediatric Research Initiative Fund. </p> <p>The National Institutes of Health (NIH) must prioritize certain pediatric research that does not replicate existing NIH research activities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
